			"condition": "dt.now.isInRange('8/18', '12/21')",
			"prompt": "Good question. I think you should maybe spend the day thinking about what the solstice means to you. <break size='0.3'/> To me it makes me think about the endless celestial <anim cat='dance' filter='&(music, short),!(robotic)' nonBlocking='true'/> dance.",
